['The goal is to create a 5 card series,the first player or team to do this wins the game.The board contains a thumbnail image for each card in the deck.Once the game starts the first player lays down a card and places a chip on the board representing the card.Then picks up a new card from the deck and then the next player takes a turn.Players can strategically place chips to block the others. There are a few twists and turns in the game that pump up the fun, like the one-eyed and two-eyed Jacks', 'Easy to learn fun to play! A strategy game which is fun to play. It requires tactical thinking, but simple to learn. You can have 2-3 teams of single players or multiple players.There is some strategy to the game if you want to win, but the element of chance plays a huge role in this game.There are very few rules and the game easy to learn; easy to play. After playing a couple times that you can proficient and learning some strategy.', 'A combination of card and board game with lots of strategy. This game is fun because you can play strategically with advanced players or go easily on new players to let them learn and not smash their spirits. We had lots of fun playing this with teams of larger groups or with just two people.', "Suitable for team or family play ---- Board Game for 2 -12 players, ages 7 and up, classic strategy card board game. board game is excellent for multi-generational families. An 8 year old child will have as much fun as an an 80 year old great grandmother! Can be enjoyed by players of multiple ages since it's easy enough for kids and adults had lots of fun too.", "Package Includes:Folding Game Board, 2 Decks of Playing Poker Cards, 135 Playing Chips and Instructions, Game Instructions. Tips:the game usually goes quite quickly (less than one hour). It's a board game to play with your family and friends as you will really enjoy it!"]
